	<express_ref linkend="Draughting_element_specialisations:arm:Draughting_element_specialisations_arm.Dimension_value"/>
	that presents information associated with a dimension, 
	in which individual elements presenting different components of the dimensional information may be identified and distinguished.
	<example>
		<p>
		<module_ref linkend="draughting_element_specialisations:4_entities:figure:sdc">
		Figure 2</module_ref>
		illustrates components of a structured dimension callout.
		</p>
		<figure id="sdc" number="2">
			<title>Structured dimension callout</title>
			<img src="Structured_dimension_callout.gif"/>
		</figure>
	</example>
</ext_description>

